value: Iberian Peninsula, Morocco, Tunisia, Algeria and Libya

Southern Spain and North Africa from southern Morocco to northern Tunisia, recently spreading farther east to Cyre- naica. Migrates through the western Sahara to the savannas of West Africa from Senegal to northern Nigeria.
